						{3 mul HiVal mul round cvi 1 add Lookup exch get HiVal div}exch addprocs 4 1 roll
						{3 mul HiVal mul round cvi 		Lookup exch get HiVal div}exch addprocs 4 1 roll
						setcolortransfer 
